=Reseat the LCD Backlight Cable= 
----
====If the screen of your Cr-48 suddenly goes dark it may be that the ribbon cable attaching the backlight to the motherboard has simply worked loose.==== 
====Follow this guide to reseat and secure the cable to correct this problem.==== 
# ====Open the Cr-48 case by following the guide [[Open the Cr-48|here]]==== 
# ====Identify the LCD connector using the photograph below. It is under a small piece of black fabric tape.==== 
# ====Gently remove the connector from its receptacle and then gently push it back in==== 
# ====To prevent the connection from becoming loose again you can apply a small amount of hot glue behind the connection==== 
# ====Reassemble the case==== 

Source: [[http://www.chromeoslounge.com/cr-48-chrome-notebook/2920-lcd-backlight-failure-fix.html]]

